Although many of these issues are directed to a plaintiff, we too will need 
to take positions on many of these items, particularly Nos. (3) & (7) - 
(10).? We also need to better understand the nature of the dispute and our 
strategy going forward.

I would like to set up a conference call for Monday, May 1, 2000 at 11:00 
a.m. (PST) to discuss the foregoing.? Please let me know if this time is 
convenient for you.

